      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014I've babied it from day one and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. If you're looking for a car that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and kept in pristine condition, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 43500.0,
