      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six remains mechanically pristine, featuring a recently serviced VANOS system and verified subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains its original geometry with zero bushing deflection, ensuring the sharp turn-in and telepathic feedback these chassis are known for. Every individual throttle body is synchronized to perfection, providing immediate transient throttle response. This is a collector-grade specimen with a documented service history and flawless mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
