    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a flawless factory finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, showing absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats are supple without any bolster wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history exclusively through authorized dealerships and zero modifications. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. This is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
